SkillAdded(uint256).notice: emitted when a new skill is added to the database by the admin;

SkillGroupAdded(uint256).notice: emitted when a new skill group is added to the database by the admin;

SkillRemoved(uint256).notice: emitted when a new skill is removed from the database by the admin;

addSkill((bool,uint8,uint8,string,string.notice: adds a new skill to the database of trainable skills and adds it to a skill group

addSkillGroup((uint256,string)).notice: adds a new skill group to the database

getSkillById(uint256).notice: get a Skill struct by id

removeSkill(uint256).notice: removes a skill from the database and removes it from the skillgroup
